    <h1 class="display-3">Welcome! Log in below:</h1>
    <p class="lead">Let's Have Fun Together is the Premier Event Planning App</p>
    <p class="lead"><strong>To explore the app, use "demo" for login and password.</strong></p>
    <p class="lead"><em>Unfortunately, events and information in the app are not kept updated</em></p>

      <%= form_for @user, url: login_path, method: :post do |f| %>
        <%= f.label :username %>
